/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a high angle, providing a comprehensive view of the street below. The street is flanked by buildings and trees, creating a harmonious blend of urban and natural elements. The buildings, painted in shades of white and gray, stand tall against the overcast sky. The trees, on the other hand, add a touch of green to the urban landscape. Overhead, power lines crisscross the sky, a common sight in many cities. A car can be seen driving down the street, adding a dynamic element to the otherwise static scene. The colors in the image are muted, reflecting the overcast weather conditions.
